igers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"serious risk\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"almost every Summer Games\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"its introduction\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, the only year it has not made an appearance was 1912, when laws in Sweden prohibited the sport.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.8313268722175406, \"rank\": 0.1725663289145935, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only year\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"an appearance\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"laws\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Boxing Association (IBA) was stripped of its status as the global governing body for boxing by the Intentional Olympic Committee (IOC) in June 2023 after it failed to complete reforms on governance, finance and ethical issues.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2040864568616156e-24, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9977267670086785, \"rank\": 0.0022783916237953065, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its status\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"the global governing body\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"the Intentional Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"IOC\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"reforms\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"governance\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"finance\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"ethical issues\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking ahead to 2028, the IOC have warned that boxing has little chance of featuring unless it proves that it has cleaned up its act amid allegations of corruption, match-fixing and financial scandals.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3925423282303573e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"little chance\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"its act\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"allegations\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"match-fixing and financial scandals\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson, who claimed Team's sole boxing medal in Paris with bronze in the men's light middleweight category, hopes a resolution is found so that aspiring fighters are given the same platform that has benefitted him in his career.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9946872821664631, \"rank\": 0.00534109355645238, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999979982022, \"rank\": 2.001724540308603e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team's sole boxing medal\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's light middleweight category\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"a resolution\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"aspiring fighters\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"the same platform\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'To the athletes, to the boxers in general, I think it's extremely damaging,' Richardson told BBC Sport.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9946872821664631, \"rank\": 0.00534109355645238, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9978784384113851, \"rank\": 0.0014633740997712897, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxers\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Olympic Games just puts you on such a global platform.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"such a global platform\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the biggest stage in the world, it gives you a real opportunity to showcase your skills in front of everybody.'\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest stage\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"a real opportunity\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"your skills\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson added: 'From an athlete perspective, it would be extremely damaging.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9946872821664631, \"rank\": 0.00534109355645238, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete perspective\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'From a sporting, from an Olympic, from a UK Sport perspective, if boxing is not to be in LA I believe it would be an absolute travesty because boxing is such a special sport, it's historical.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sporting\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"an absolute travesty\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"such a special sport\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'People love the gladiatorial aspect of boxing where men and women compete one-on-one to see who is victorious.\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the gladiatorial aspect\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'As I said, it would be a real shame so let us hope World Boxing and the IOC can get together and make sure it does remain in LA because without boxing, the Olympic would certainly be missing a massive sport.'\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3925423282303573e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real shame\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"World Boxing\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive sport\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson is eternally 'grateful' for the 'unlimited opportunities and experiences' boxing has provided him in his career and is desperate for the sport to remain part of the Olympics in LA.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2418, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9946872821664631, \"rank\": 0.00534109355645238, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 'unlimited opportunities\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"experiences' boxing\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'For me personally, boxing has changed my life for the massive, massive benefit.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"the massive, massive benefit\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have come from fairly humble beginnings and boxing has provided unlimited opportunities and experiences for me,' he continued.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fairly humble beginnings\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"unlimited opportunities\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"experiences\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have had some of the best moments of my life, including the last few weeks here at the Olympic Games, through boxing and that's why I keep saying I am so grateful.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best moments\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few weeks\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am grateful for boxing, I am grateful for the sport in general, and for me personally and for all the aspiring athletes, boxers coming through, let us hope we can do whatever we can to ensure it does remain in LA.'\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"all the aspiring athletes\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"boxers\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC have encouraged national boxing federations to create a new global body or risk missing out on the Games in 2028.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3213, \"end\": 3216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3925423282303573e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"national boxing federations